      "info.s8.linux": "Same as Windows (<kbd>Alt</kbd> and <kbd>Ctrl</kbd>). If an <kbd>Alt</kbd>+letter opens a browser menu, rebind that shortcut from the popup.",
      "info.footer": "Remember to disable the old extensions (MxM Tools Final and MxM Lyrics Compare) to avoid duplicated buttons and shortcuts.",
      "info.fn.unir": "Joins the current line with the previous one.",
      "info.fn.split": "Splits the line at the cursor position.",
      "info.fn.unirParens": "Like Join lines, but the joined text stays in parentheses. A checkbox picks uppercase/lowercase.",
      "info.fn.wrapParens": "Wraps the SELECTED text in parentheses; its checkbox picks uppercase or lowercase for the first letter.",
      "info.fn.wrapQuestion": "Wraps the SELECTED text in ¿ ?; its checkbox picks uppercase or lowercase for the first letter.",
      "info.fn.wrapExclaim": "Wraps the SELECTED text in ¡ !; its checkbox picks uppercase or lowercase for the first letter.",
      "info.s4.flashNote": "<strong>Tip:</strong> for the Gems to work well, pick a <strong>Flash</strong> model (Flash 3.5 or newer). The <strong>Pro</strong> model takes too long and sometimes misbehaves.",
      "info.s5.li5": "<strong>New:</strong> select text and <strong>right-click</strong> to add it to a highlighter list from the browser's context menu.",
      "info.s5.li6": "<strong>Manage lists and items from the popup:</strong> add or remove the words/phrases of each list, create or delete lists, and edit the <em>opened songs</em> list (view, remove, or add a song by hand).",
      "info.fn.wordCounter": "Select text, then press ⌘A/Ctrl+A twice quickly: the 2nd press shows words/characters while you hold it. ⌥X toggles the counter.",
      "info.fn.gem": "With text selected, finds the video and sends it to the transcription Gem.",
